resources.description:
*Nutrition:*

non-pregnant women (aged 15-49 years)](https://www.who.int/data/gho/data/indicators/indicator-details/GHO/mean-hemoglobin-level-of-non-pregnant-women-%28aged-15-49-years%29), [Mean hemoglobin level of
